{"tid":858423,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鯰魚扮石斑　屯門食肆男東主女經理違反商品條例被捕","createTime":"2018-10-11T20:37:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-12T09:20:48.000Z","uid":121464,"like":54,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"9d850ae36f9f2a73d6199a6522978c0dba15ea18","tid":858423,"uid":121464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T20:37:52.000Z","msg":"香港海關於本月9日拘捕一名食肆男東主及一名女經理，他們涉嫌供應附有虛假商品說明的食物，違反《商品說明條例》。<br />\n<br />\n　　海關早前接獲舉報後，前往一間位於屯門的食肆試購焗芝士石斑飯。<br />\n<br />\n　　政府化驗所檢測證實該款食物中的魚塊為鯰魚，與所宣稱的不符。<br />\n<br />\n　　經調查後，海關拘捕一名60歲男東主及一名55歲女經理。<br />\n<br />\n　　案件仍在調查中。<br />\n<br />\n　　海關提醒商戶遵守《條例》的規定，而消費者於購買商品時亦應光顧信譽良好的商戶。<br />\n<br />\n垃圾淡水魚VS海魚 所以出來絕對唔會叫魚塊飯 班腩都唔會😞😞😞"},{"pid":"82e15b815c5ef13650b5e1c787c1de6bb1690a4b","tid":858423,"uid":82028,"like":19,"dislike":2,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T20:52:19.000Z","msg":"我西貢班兄弟唔係好歡迎你班洪興仔呀！"},{"pid":"dfe8ce9d6860daf0a1ee0a4452db641fd2a15be7","tid":858423,"uid":511,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T20:59:53.000Z","msg":"拉得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d68938e64fd42f7ec52d69762d658f4244dcff7","tid":858423,"uid":52595,"like":2,"dislike":35,"score":-33,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T22:49:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e4f94cc85e3b10379d9c88c67fa7677db00eb3b4","tid":858423,"uid":140094,"like":80,"dislike":3,"score":77,"quote":{"pid":"9d68938e64fd42f7ec52d69762d658f4244dcff7","tid":858423,"uid":52595,"like":2,"dislike":35,"score":-33,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T22:49:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T22:51:33.000Z","msg":"你個名真係無改錯<br />\n符合商品說明條例<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5ed0a120ad3ab08d4381b7cccabff1745120ee3","tid":858423,"uid":67298,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"9d68938e64fd42f7ec52d69762d658f4244dcff7","tid":858423,"uid":52595,"like":2,"dislike":35,"score":-33,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T22